reviewText:
Excellent DVD...very high quality picture. Tina is at first shown working out with weights etc.
Then, the main part of the DVD - 2 wrestling matches against female opponents.
Both are good matches, very competitive with Tina looking fantastic, especially in her lilac trunks.....

If you like great unscripted mat action.you will like this video.
I am big tina moretti,fan and have enjoyed watching her wrestle always under all names.
Loved seeing her put her skill to work.
